---
title: Zucchini & Feta Fritter Pita Pockets with Feta, Creamy Dill Sauce & Arugula Salad
description: It’s hard NOT to love any ingredient when it’s fritter-fied, aka fried until perfectly golden. This version stars grated zucchini, which we fold into a light-as-air tempura batter with garlic powder, fresh dill, and salty feta. The fritters are shallow-fried pancake-style until crispy, then stuffed into warm pita pockets with tomato, arugula, and a creamy herb sauce. Talk about pita perfection!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/60eef4799848223a701e777f-8f7dfe2d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/zucchini-feta-fritter-pita-pockets-60eef4799848223a701e777f-c92ca515.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/zucchini-and-feta-fritter-pita-pockets-60eef4799848223a701e777f
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
